subject: Jockeys, Drivers and Trainers
Horse Racing
Sports Injuries
lead_paragraph: Ramon Dominguez, the reigning Eclipse Award winner for jockey of the year, was upgraded to stable condition over the weekend after fracturing his skull Friday in a race.
